    "The predicted kinase profiling results of CHMFL-BMX-078 by KIPP were overall consistent with the experimental kinases inhibition results (Additional file 2: Table S10), with an AUC ConclusionsIn this paper, we provided a comprehensive assessment of the performance of five ML (NB, RF, XGBoost, KNN, and SVM) and seven DL (DNN, GCN, GAT, MPNN, D-MPNN, Attentive FP, and FP-GNN) methods in kinase profiling prediction task.",
